name: Race to the Center of the Universe
Race Through the Planet of the Monsters

description:
Sam (Jared Padalecki) and Dean (Jensen Ackles) follow the coordinates left in their father's journal and land in the middle of the woods where they investigate the disappearance of several campers. The two brothers soon learn they are dealing with a Wendigo, a creature made famous in Native America legends. A Wendigo is a former human whose cannibalism has transformed him into a creature with superhuman strength and speed that feasts on human flesh.

Eric Kripke wrote the episode directed by David Nutter.
name: Wendigo

deck: Robin is tasked with watching the Batcave while Batman is away, however his friends come and ruin his task.
name: Sidekick

deck: After succumbing to pressure Raven uses her powers to fix her friends problems however, the more she uses them she becomes more and more evil.
name: Nose Mouth

deck: The FF reveals their origin story.
description:
The Fantastic Four joins a telethon for education and they're going to tell us their origin story. Reed Richards asked the aid of his companions, Ben Grimm, Sue and Johnny Storm in order to investigate a bizarre phenomenon in space. After they get their powers, they're gonna have to save the Thing from Puppet Master, a puppeteer kind of guy who uses radioactive clay to control people's minds. Will the FF save the day? Will they ever get enough money for charity?

Note: This episode is a direct adaptation and combination of Fantastic Four Issues #1 until #8.
name: The Origin of the Fantastic Four: Part 1

description:
The story continues on the telethon, starring the Fantastic Four! Alicia Masters learns of his stepfather's crimes. The Puppet Master starts a jail break while pursuing his vision of ruling the world. Lucky for them, the Thing is free from mind control and they will stop him before he becomes king. Back at the studio, the Thing still tries to convince the audience to donate as the amount of money increases.

Note: This episode is a direct adaptation and combination of Fantastic Four Issues #1 until #8.
name: The Origin of the Fantastic Four: Part 2

description: After escaping from strange new foes. The Maximals awake unable to transform, the four surviving Maximals encounter a mysterious supercomputer which remakes them into a new kind of Transformers.
name: The Reformatting

description: After their learning how to transform again they gain access to the Council Citadel, the amnesiac Maximals learn that Megatron has taken over Cybertron!
name: Master of the House

description: After being defeated by his Maximal foes, Megatron brings three new Generals online, and sends them after the Maximals while they are searching for their missing memories.
name: Fires of the Past

description: Trigger (), Higane)
name: Trigger

description: The Maximals have a second run-in with the Vehicon generals, and sense the presence of a familiar spark. Rattrap discovers a counter-virus that helps him Transform but once he starts, he can't stop.
name: Mercenary Pursuits

description: A mysterious bat named Nightscream offers a strange new energy supply, but is it a blessing or a curse?
name: Forbidden Fruit

description: Frustrated by his transformation and ashamed of his uselessness, Rattrap makes a deal with Megatron!
name: The Weak Component

description: The Maximals discover a junkyard with robotic shells of former transformers, and Blackarachnia learns more about the Vehicon general, Thrust.
name: Revelations Part I: Discovery

description: Cheetor and Rattrap leads a dangerous mission to try to bring out Tankor's old Maximal personality and make a surprising discovery about their missing memories and the identity of Tankor.
name: Revelations Part II: Descent

description: Nightscream pursues Jetstorm, who has captured Blackarachnia's spark; meanwhile, Optimus tries to bring Rhinox back to the Maximals side.
name: Revelations Part III: Apocalypse

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Megatron targets Nightscream for capture, so he can learn more about how the Maximal was able to survive a techno-virus.
name: Survivor

description: Rhinox discovers an ancient weapon with the power to turn organic material into cybernetic metal.
name: The Key

description: Rattrap uses a catalyst program to accelerate the growth of Cybertron's new found plant life. Meanwhile Blackarachnia learns the truth about Thrust.
name: The Catalyst

description: Megatron and Optimus are set to go head to head with doomsday weapons, and both seem willing to destroy Cybertron to gain victory.
name: End of the Line
Don't Toy With Me on a Whim

description: After releasing a doomsday weapon, Optimus must face the consequences of his actions. After realizing that the oracle sent them to Earth to bring back organic life, for there to be a balance between technology and organic.
name: Fallout

description: While trying to recruit the Vehicons, the Maximals discover two strange new organic creatures, but what secrets do they hide?
name: Savage Noble

description: The Maximals infiltrate Megatron's fortress, but their new friend has a different idea.
name: Prometheus Unbound

description: Blackarachnia is finally able to revive Silverbolt, but he doesn't seem too happy about it.
name: In Darkest Knight

description: Megatron unleashes a new virus that turns the Maximals into their own worst enemies. Just as Optimus has second thoughts about his plan for harmony.
name: A Wolf in the Fold

description: A spaceship crash-lands on Cybertron, releasing a tentacled alien monster. The Maximals and Vehicons both rush to take control of the vessel's secrets.
name: Home Soil

description: While searching for the missing sparks, the Maximals are attacked by two new Vehicon generals who are not exactly as they appear!
name: Sparkwar Part 1: The Strike

description: Desperate to thwart Megatron, the Maximals continue their search for the missing sparks.
name: Sparkwar Part 2: The Search

description: Having found the imprisoned sparks, the Maximals have to race against time to stop Megatron from achieving his ultimate Ascension.
name: Sparkwar Part 3: The Siege

description: Megatron has been defeated, but strange creatures keep attacking the Maximals all over Cybertron something horrible haunts the entire planet!
name: Spark of Darkness
